---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Intelligence | Levenhall" description="Levenhall Intelligence is a live defense and geopolitical operating picture — 119 feeds, on-device ML, and a proprietary instability index on one WebGL globe. Live at intel.levenhall.com.">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="i-hero">
        <div class="i-hero-bg"></div>
        <div class="i-hero-grid"></div>
        <div class="i-hero-scan"></div>

        <span class="i-hud i-hud-tl"></span>
        <span class="i-hud i-hud-tr"></span>
        <span class="i-hud i-hud-bl"></span>
        <span class="i-hud i-hud-br"></span>

        <div class="i-hero-inner">
            <p class="i-tag">A Levenhall Product</p>
            <p class="i-pre">Levenhall</p>
            <h1 class="i-wordmark">INTELLIGENCE</h1>
            <p class="i-tagline">A live operating picture for defense &amp; geopolitics.</p>

            <div class="i-hero-meta">
                <span class="i-meta-dot"></span>
                <span class="i-meta-text">Live at <a href="https://intel.levenhall.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">intel.levenhall.com</a></span>
            </div>

            <div class="i-cta">
                <a href="https://intel.levenhall.com" class="btn btn-gold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open the Dashboard</a>
                <a href="#how" class="btn btn-outline-white">How It Works</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── OPENING ── -->
    <section class="i-section i-opening">
        <div class="i-narrow reveal">
            <p class="i-lede">Every signal an allied analyst would want, fused into one screen. <strong>Nothing leaves the browser.</strong></p>
            <p>Levenhall Intelligence is a dashboard we built to operate the way analysts actually work &mdash; one tab, every layer, on a globe that updates in real time. Conflict events, civil unrest, military movements, infrastructure status, economic indicators, climate anomalies, live media. The heavy machine learning &mdash; embeddings, sentiment, summarization, named entity recognition &mdash; runs in a Web Worker on the analyst's own device. No round-trip to a server. No data leakage.</p>
            <p class="i-opening-close">It is also the most public demonstration of what Levenhall builds. Open it in a browser; the rest of this page explains what you'll see.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── THE CII (HERO MOMENT WITH FORMULA) ── -->
    <section class="i-section i-cii">
        <div class="i-cii-bg"></div>
        <div class="i-cii-inner">
            <div class="i-cii-head reveal">
                <span class="i-eyebrow">§ The proprietary layer</span>
                <h2>The Country Instability Index.</h2>
                <p>A composite 0&ndash;100 score across thirty-one Tier-1 countries &mdash; the nations most relevant to allied defense posture. Conflict, unrest, information, and security signals, weighted and modified for each country's baseline.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="i-formula reveal">
                <span class="i-formula-label">Blended Score</span>
                <pre class="i-formula-code">
<span class="i-fc-bracket">(</span><span class="i-fc-var">Baseline Risk</span> <span class="i-fc-op">×</span> <span class="i-fc-num">0.4</span><span class="i-fc-bracket">)</span> <span class="i-fc-op">+</span> <span class="i-fc-bracket">(</span><span class="i-fc-var">Event Score</span> <span class="i-fc-op">×</span> <span class="i-fc-num">0.6</span><span class="i-fc-bracket">)</span>
<span class="i-fc-op">+</span> <span class="i-fc-var">Hotspot Boost</span>
<span class="i-fc-op">+</span> <span class="i-fc-var">News Urgency Boost</span>
<span class="i-fc-op">+</span> <span class="i-fc-var">Focal Point Boost</span>
<span class="i-fc-op">+</span> <span class="i-fc-var">Displacement Boost</span>
<span class="i-fc-op">+</span> <span class="i-fc-var">Climate Stress</span></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="i-cii-foot reveal">
                <p>The Event Score itself is weighted: <span class="i-tag-inline i-tag-conf">Conflict 30%</span> <span class="i-tag-inline i-tag-unr">Unrest 25%</span> <span class="i-tag-inline i-tag-inf">Information 25%</span> <span class="i-tag-inline i-tag-sec">Security 20%</span>. Active wars score 70 or higher automatically. A million displaced adds 8. Each country carries a multiplier from 0.3× to 3× to compensate for media suppression and expected event frequency.</p>
                <p class="i-tier-row">
                    Output:
                    <span class="i-tier i-tier-low">Low</span>
                    <span class="i-tier-arrow">›</span>
                    <span class="i-tier i-tier-norm">Normal</span>
                    <span class="i-tier-arrow">›</span>
                    <span class="i-tier i-tier-elev">Elevated</span>
                    <span class="i-tier-arrow">›</span>
                    <span class="i-tier i-tier-high">High</span>
                    <span class="i-tier-arrow">›</span>
                    <span class="i-tier i-tier-crit">Critical</span>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── HOW IT WORKS — EDITORIAL ── -->
    <section class="i-section i-how" id="how">
        <div class="i-how-inner reveal">
            <span class="i-eyebrow">§ Around the index</span>
            <h2>Five more layers, briefly.</h2>

            <div class="i-how-grid">
                <article class="i-how-item">
                    <span class="i-how-num">02</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Geo-Convergence</h3>
                        <p>The globe split into 1&deg; grid cells. Multi-source signal convergence inside a 24-hour rolling window. Conflict, protest, military, and news signals clustering in one cell triggers a hotspot &mdash; before mainstream reporting catches up.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="i-how-item">
                    <span class="i-how-num">03</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Strategic Risk Composite</h3>
                        <p>One score per region. Geo-convergence at thirty percent, CII at fifty, infrastructure cascade risk at twenty. The single number an executive needs.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="i-how-item">
                    <span class="i-how-num">04</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Signal Bridge</h3>
                        <p>A unified bus that ingests conflict, unrest, economy, cyber, military, and climate streams &mdash; and routes prioritized signals across modules and into the wider Levenhall stack.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="i-how-item">
                    <span class="i-how-num">05</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>On-Device ML</h3>
                        <p>Four ONNX models in a Web Worker: MiniLM for embeddings, DistilBERT for sentiment, FLAN-T5 for summarization, BERT for named-entity recognition. Two-hundred-megabyte budget. Zero server roundtrips.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="i-how-item">
                    <span class="i-how-num">06</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Cascade Analysis</h3>
                        <p>Models the dependencies between undersea cables, power grids, pipelines, and data centers. One disruption tells you what falls next.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── THE MAP & COVERAGE ── -->
    <section class="i-section i-map">
        <div class="i-narrow reveal">
            <span class="i-eyebrow">§ The globe</span>
            <h2>34 layers on a WebGL globe. 31 countries you can drill into.</h2>
            <p class="i-map-lede">DeckGL and MapLibre underneath. Eleven layers default on &mdash; conflicts, military assets, sanctions, hotspots, nuclear facilities, waterways, infrastructure outages, natural disasters, economic indicators, weather. Twenty-three more a click away &mdash; undersea cables, pipelines, AIS tracking, military flights, cyber threats, displacement camps, financial centers, and the rest.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="i-coverage reveal">
            <div class="i-cov-row">
                <span class="i-cov-cat i-cov-cat-allied">NATO &amp; Allied</span>
                <span class="i-cov-flags">🇺🇸 🇬🇧 🇫🇷 🇩🇪 🇵🇱 🇦🇺</span>
            </div>
            <div class="i-cov-row">
                <span class="i-cov-cat i-cov-cat-adv">Adversarial</span>
                <span class="i-cov-flags">🇷🇺 🇨🇳 🇮🇷 🇰🇵</span>
            </div>
            <div class="i-cov-row">
                <span class="i-cov-cat i-cov-cat-conf">Active Conflict</span>
                <span class="i-cov-flags">🇺🇦 🇸🇾 🇾🇪 🇲🇲 🇸🇩 🇪🇹 🇨🇩 🇸🇴 🇦🇫 🇮🇶 🇱🇾 🇳🇬 🇱🇧</span>
            </div>
            <div class="i-cov-row">
                <span class="i-cov-cat i-cov-cat-reg">Strategic Powers</span>
                <span class="i-cov-flags">🇮🇳 🇵🇰 🇸🇦 🇹🇷 🇦🇪 🇧🇷 🇻🇪 🇹🇼</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── CTA ── -->
    <section class="i-cta-section">
        <div class="i-cta-bg"></div>
        <div class="i-cta-inner">
            <span class="i-cta-dot"></span>
            <p class="i-cta-eyebrow">Live Now</p>
            <h2>Open the dashboard.</h2>
            <p>Email-gated. Free to enter. Bespoke deployments available through Levenhall's intelligence practice.</p>
            <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
                <a href="https://intel.levenhall.com" class="btn btn-gold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">intel.levenhall.com</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-white">Contact Levenhall</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
    /* ── HERO ── */
    .i-hero {
        background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, #0c2540 0%, #060c18 70%, #03060d 100%);
        padding: 9rem 2rem 5.5rem;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        min-height: 78vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .i-hero-bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 40%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08) 0%, transparent 55%),
            radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.18) 0%, transparent 50%);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .i-hero-grid {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            linear-gradient(rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 80px 80px;
        pointer-events: none;
        mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 25%, transparent 75%);
        -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 25%, transparent 75%);
    }

    .i-hero-scan {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 50%, transparent 50%);
        background-size: 100% 3px;
        pointer-events: none;
        mix-blend-mode: overlay;
        opacity: 0.4;
    }

    .i-hud {
        position: absolute;
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        border: 2px solid var(--gold);
        opacity: 0.55;
    }
    .i-hud-tl { top: 24px; left: 24px; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; }
    .i-hud-tr { top: 24px; right: 24px; border-left: none; border-bottom: none; }
    .i-hud-bl { bottom: 24px; left: 24px; border-right: none; border-top: none; }
    .i-hud-br { bottom: 24px; right: 24px; border-left: none; border-top: none; }

    .i-hero::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, var(--gold) 50%, transparent 100%);
        opacity: 0.55;
    }

    .i-hero-inner {
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .i-tag {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.66rem;
        letter-spacing: 3.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }

    .i-pre {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        letter-spacing: 6px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
        margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
        text-indent: 6px;
    }

    .i-wordmark {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 10px;
        color: #fff;
        line-height: 1;
        margin: 0 0 1.4rem;
        text-indent: 10px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 30%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.7) 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .i-tagline {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .i-hero-meta {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.6rem;
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        padding: 0.45rem 0.9rem;
        background: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.15);
    }

    .i-meta-dot {
        width: 7px;
        height: 7px;
        background: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.9);
        border-radius: 50%;
        box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.6);
        animation: i-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes i-pulse {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
        50% { opacity: 0.4; }
    }

    .i-meta-text a {
        color: var(--gold);
        text-decoration: none;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .i-meta-text a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .i-cta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    /* ── SHARED ── */
    .i-section {
        padding: 6rem 0;
    }

    .i-narrow {
        max-width: 660px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .i-eyebrow {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        letter-spacing: 2.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    /* ── OPENING ── */
    .i-opening {
        background: var(--cream);
        padding: 6rem 0;
    }

    .i-lede {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        line-height: 1.45;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .i-lede strong {
        color: var(--burgundy);
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .i-opening p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .i-opening-close {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 1.15rem !important;
        color: var(--burgundy) !important;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
        padding-top: 1.4rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    /* ── CII (HERO MOMENT) ── */
    .i-cii {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a1628 0%, var(--deep-navy) 100%);
        padding: 6.5rem 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .i-cii-bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 30%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%),
            radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 70%, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.04) 0%, transparent 50%);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .i-cii::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3);
    }

    .i-cii-inner {
        max-width: 820px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .i-cii-head {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .i-cii-head h2 {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem);
        line-height: 1.2;
        color: #fff;
        margin: 0 0 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .i-cii-head p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .i-formula {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
        padding: 2.2rem 2.4rem;
        margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
        max-width: 680px;
    }

    .i-formula-label {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 2.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .i-formula-code {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', 'Consolas', monospace;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 2;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
        white-space: pre;
        overflow-x: auto;
    }

    .i-fc-var {
        color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.9);
    }

    .i-fc-num {
        color: var(--gold);
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .i-fc-op,
    .i-fc-bracket {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    }

    .i-cii-foot {
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .i-cii-foot p {
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
        margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    }

    .i-tag-inline {
        display: inline-block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        padding: 0.18rem 0.55rem;
        margin: 0.1rem 0.15rem;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .i-tag-conf { background: rgba(161, 62, 10, 0.18); color: #d77a40; border: 1px solid rgba(161, 62, 10, 0.3); }
    .i-tag-unr { background: rgba(139, 21, 56, 0.18); color: #d8638a; border: 1px solid rgba(139, 21, 56, 0.3); }
    .i-tag-inf { background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.15); color: var(--gold); border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); }
    .i-tag-sec { background: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.1); color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.9); border: 1px solid rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.25); }

    .i-tier-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        margin-top: 1.4rem;
        padding-top: 1.4rem;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .i-tier {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 0.22rem 0.6rem;
    }

    .i-tier-low { color: #6da17a; background: rgba(109, 161, 122, 0.12); }
    .i-tier-norm { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
    .i-tier-elev { color: var(--gold); background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.12); }
    .i-tier-high { color: #d77a40; background: rgba(161, 62, 10, 0.18); }
    .i-tier-crit { color: #ff5c7c; background: rgba(255, 92, 124, 0.15); }

    .i-tier-arrow {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    /* ── HOW IT WORKS ── */
    .i-how {
        background: var(--cream);
    }

    .i-how-inner {
        max-width: 820px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .i-how h2 {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.3rem);
        line-height: 1.25;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 2.4rem;
    }

    .i-how-grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .i-how-item {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        padding: 1.8rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.1);
    }

    .i-how-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }

    .i-how-num {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--gold);
        line-height: 1;
        text-align: right;
        padding-top: 0.3rem;
    }

    .i-how-item h3 {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
    }

    .i-how-item p {
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* ── MAP & COVERAGE ── */
    .i-map {
        background: var(--stone);
    }

    .i-map h2 {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.8vw, 2.1rem);
        line-height: 1.3;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .i-map-lede {
        font-size: 1.02rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin: 0;
    }

    .i-coverage {
        max-width: 820px;
        margin: 3rem auto 0;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .i-cov-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        padding: 1.2rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.1);
        align-items: center;
    }

    .i-cov-row:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }

    .i-cov-cat {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 700;
